data.description: Welcome to your open-concept, bright and sparkling NEW home. This Lily model has upgrades galore with luxury vinyl flooring throughout the entire main floor, an extended kitchen with white cabinets, large island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, large eating space and upgraded light fixtures. The rest of the spacious main level has a living room area that can also be used as a formal dining room, playroom or office space along with an updated half bath and big family room area. The upstairs boasts a large master bedroom suite that has a master bath with a soaking tub, separate shower and double sinks and a walk-in closet with tons of hanging space and shelving. Also on the 2nd level are the additional three spacious bedrooms along with another full bathroom with a tub & shower and a convenient full laundry room area. There is also a full unfinished basement area awaiting your finishing touches along with a 3-car attached garage.  Don't forget about the cute front porch and cement patio area in the backyard surrounded by a fully sodded yard along with the installed sprinkler system. Beautiful home ready for you to move right in and in a fabulous location near schools, parks, restaurants, shopping and all of the Village of New Lenox amenities.
